rom the start! So I'm planning how I'd like to phrase that.\"}]}"},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] Hello — I’m LoopAI Patient Agent, here to help you think through symptoms, track health information, or review prior medical details in a calm, structured way. What would you like to do today?","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0c6d773fcaebd05f0169b41ac66978819183f89d143437ef68\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":2154,"output":74,"cacheRead":8192,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":10420,"cost":{"input":0.005385,"output":0.00111,"cacheRead":0.002048,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.008543}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773411011241}}
